{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","title":"寒蝉效应","desc":"","updated":1646881366327,"created":1645096787928,"custom":{},"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"5f3cc01b0ef0473cbfa2b1bca74aaaeb","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"censorship.coercion","alias":"胁迫","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":8,"offset":8},"end":{"line":2,"column":36,"offset":36},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"censorship.coercion"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"自我审查","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":64,"offset":64},"end":{"line":2,"column":72,"offset":72},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"自我审查"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"censorship.surveillance","alias":"监视","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":115,"offset":200},"end":{"line":6,"column":147,"offset":232},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"censorship.surveillance"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.OverseasChinese","alias":"#OverseasChinese","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":448},"end":{"line":13,"column":17,"offset":464},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.OverseasChinese"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.Comic","alias":"#Comic","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":18,"offset":465},"end":{"line":13,"column":24,"offset":471},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.Comic"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.psychology.chillingeffect","id":"N88O88m73mmDsfq7AfXGa","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.FreeSpeech","alias":"#FreeSpeech","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":25,"offset":472},"end":{"line":13,"column":36,"offset":483},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.FreeSpeech"}}],"anchors":{"暴露ip地址":{"type":"header","text":"暴露IP地址","value":"暴露ip地址","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"治罪":{"type":"header","text":"治罪","value":"治罪","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"7w0Rte16ynjy1n8BCmB35","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"寒蝉效应\">寒蝉效应<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#寒蝉效应\"></a></h1>\n<p>寒蝉效应是透过<a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/YA9otcqln5hfxZTLkt5XV\">胁迫</a>等手段，让人们在发表言论之前就产生心惊胆战的感觉，或自动<a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">自我审查 (Private)</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"暴露ip地址\">暴露IP地址<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#暴露ip地址\"></a></h2>\n<p>大约在2021年下半年左右（没有具体的日期），墙内的服务开始出现越来越的暴露IP地址的情况。这种情况与互联网早期的论坛显示用户的地址（地址的一部分会用*来打码保护隐私）不同，而是根据上下文是否有敏感词而让发言的用户感觉自己在被“<a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/dfFVhq6KmXDfxCrmpO20R\">监视</a>“。 </p>\n<h2 id=\"治罪\">治罪<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#治罪\"></a></h2>\n<p>当然，审查者也会利用国家机器对自由言论和创作的行为进行惩罚。漫画作者张某宁（橘豚）<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/614670.html\">因其创作“猪头人身”系列漫画而被官方定罪并判刑一年</a>，因传播橘豚漫画，另一位网友卢世宁从境外回国时<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/658019.html\">被刑事拘留</a>。</p>\n<p><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#OverseasChinese (Private)</a> <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#Comic (Private)</a> <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#FreeSpeech (Private)</a> </p>","noteIndex":{"id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE",